{"tid":644362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藏毒「瀨屎」警判囚8個月 官: 你應該去執法，唔係去犯法","createTime":"2018-04-27T07:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T09:20:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5a20f2acb23101fa354b988f6e4989ee6d9bead2","tid":644362,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180427/large/1524813714_a326.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180427%2Flarge%2F1524813714_a326.jpg&h=5be511da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n休班高級警員晚上密會毒品疑犯後遇同袍追截，後來被搜出身藏毒品「K仔」，男警被捕後報稱「瀨屎」拒蹲下鎖手銬，及後又稱遭探員插贓嫁禍。男警早前被裁定藏毒罪成，裁判官今判被告入獄8個月，並指「你係一個警察，應該去執法，唔係去犯法！」<br />\n<br />\n被告潘俊東（40歲）被控於去年10月28日，在荃灣綠楊新邨D座旁的行人路管有危險藥物，即0.38克氯胺酮。辯方今透露，被告為了減壓於2016年開始吸毒，但今年初已停止，現時沒有毒癮，報告不建議判他入戒毒所，剩餘判刑選擇只有罰款或監禁。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指控罪非常嚴重，被告是警務人員身份令本案增添嚴重性，後來以監禁9個月為量刑起點，考慮被告當差逾20年，酌情減刑1個月，終判即時監禁8個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180427/58124935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180427%2F58124935&d=qGy8gEYPqsXYxjpZAllIvzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b92bbe54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180427%2F58124935&h=d0cd3fe9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180427/58124935</a>"},{"pid":"0d464fa4fe5fbc0cefd3e62d35d316626d121c6c","tid":644362,"uid":179547,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"點解當差成日都可以減刑，返其他工就冇？"},{"pid":"c481e498bf2d18f841e134e7789360bcb48c5fbc","tid":644362,"uid":105232,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0d464fa4fe5fbc0cefd3e62d35d316626d121c6c","tid":644362,"uid":179547,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"點解當差成日都可以減刑，返其他工就冇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:02:18.000Z","msg":"當差知法犯法，加佢老母刑就岩"},{"pid":"3afb5193c5fa1d7db0ffb437ef35a8cb17ffda0d","tid":644362,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:04:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d35f1aa05b81939f175c2e757d23a91a311fd885","tid":644362,"uid":30794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:05:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解當差成日都可以減刑，返其他工就冇？</blockquote>當差知法犯法，加佢老母刑就岩</blockquote><br />\n岩 知法犯法仲減咁樣真係講唔通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9eb939133f59f21e54c4902c240bfaf2a7b6f1","tid":644362,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"阿sir犯法唔使你教"},{"pid":"b7964f9c84f054ec05e949a4180f3f6a6e6ba9e3","tid":644362,"uid":42367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:09:07.000Z","msg":"又一分。。"},{"pid":"44f957a9dc1ed17af878cce743a86b421c5d62c0","tid":644362,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:20:15.000Z","msg":"你應該去執屎，唔係去瀨屎"}]}